data.description: Luxury living on a premier golf course and a corner lot! This home features a main level primary suite with walk in closet, free standing soaking tub, large shower and separate water closet. There’s also an additional bedroom on the main level and full bathroom for guests. The open floor plan is very welcoming and luxuriously done. The gourmet kitchen offers quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, beautiful large island and separate pantry. Another two bedrooms and a full bathroom are located upstairs with an open living area. Neighborhood offers so many extras! HOA takes care of mowing the grass and blowing the front and back porches every week, adding mulch to flower beds, cleaning the gutters, sprinkler system, termite bond and pressure washing the house. Along with a beautiful golf view you can enjoy the built in fire pit in the backyard! This home truly does have it all and will not last long! Schedule your showing today! Sqft approx; buyer to verify. Seller offering $4,000 toward buyer's closing costs w/ accepted offer.
